title: 'Internal: one tree. External: List of trees.'
pid: f77ed549-0046-4faa-8db0-0f5afc18bd2b
body: |2-
  ego_tree makes the internal representation convenient,
  because (IIRC) there are reasons to
  move nodes across trees in the viewforest.

  But representing it externally as a list of trees
  would simplify the programs that use it,
  because they often treat roots differently from higher nodes.
